UID:1juCTYY1W0b73iRq_UPxO
SUMMARY:Meet Up Magnolia- virtual networking
DTSTAMP:20260406T013622Z
DTSTART:20260611T093000Z
DESCRIPTION:Our member businesses know the value of networking. Join us for
	 our virtual networking event\\\, Meet Up Magnolia\\\, on the  2nd Thursda
	y of every month. \\nHow does this virtual networking work? You simply log
	 on to the Zoom link and will be paired into one-on-one chats for 8 to 10 
	minutes each. We will repeat the process for approximately 3 or 4 rounds. 
	You even have the option to follow up after the meeting and send a message
	 to one or more of the people you meet to keep the dialogue going. \\nSo m
	any people to meet\\\, so many professional relationships to build. Join u
	s HERE.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/meet-up-magnolia-virtual-net
	working-2024-12-12/2026-06-11/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
